{"tid":1393210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 和理非流動連儂場 之 IFC偶遇絲打s","createTime":"2019-08-01T04:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T12:52:35.000Z","uid":187489,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"280c618a05fcb7c31c66eff8e18155fbddd472c5","tid":1393210,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:20:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>文宣真係少咗，好似冇人派傳單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我都想問葵青區有冇人派傳單想幫手</blockquote>想買部平平地既投影機 係屋邨播片有冇得搞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xPeHQkj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxPeHQkj.jpg&h=5f0ad844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIFC見到有3個女仔自發用手提projector靜默播片，<br />\n右後方有保安跟住行，冇阻撓<br />\n<br />\n現場所見好多人有興趣睇，建議其他巴絲可以行下企下，因為大部份人想睇但唔會跟住邊行邊睇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以後當我地未夠人但又想幫手，又或者有骨氣嘅商場，我地咁樣做都好有用！小心有人搞事，準備隨時拍片自保<br />\n<br />\n見到就遮樣放上黎，希望達到蝴蝶效應。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Liberate Hong Kong,<br />\nthe revolution of our times.<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">流動文宣方向：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n深淺黃地方：用有禮或感性方式宣傳罷工片段<br />\n深藍淺藍中立地方：播政府暴力<br />\n大家公司後樓梯/放煙break地方：poster for 5/8<br />\n公司番放工/食lunch 必經之路：poster for 5/8 (商廈indoor 如果冇人留守一定搣，除非用IFC絲打呢招)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">播放素材：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港電台 - 《鏗鏘集》721 元朗黑夜<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/16CiwPChpr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F16CiwPChpr0&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl58WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=63c49be9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/16CiwPChpr0</a><br />\n<br />\nNow財經新聞 - 《經緯線》元朗黑夜<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B8QRzVbfLCQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB8QRzVbfLCQ&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl58WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=88007a65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B8QRzVbfLCQ</a>"},{"pid":"c10cd9a697cdf8515e3bc18902cf28dd19f031cc","tid":1393210,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"加油，85大罷工"},{"pid":"fc0c9942edaa627bb982e6ab119403c62a83f41c","tid":1393210,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:03:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7d7601937879056a20547abfb10beef93f2cf5d","tid":1393210,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:42:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05219218d7e0935080eeca82f8a81395a398ac5d","tid":1393210,"uid":66639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"蝴蝶效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ab468e885c71c50bca2d12744ac9567bf99d44","tid":1393210,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05219218d7e0935080eeca82f8a81395a398ac5d","tid":1393210,"uid":66639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"蝴蝶效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:02:08.000Z","msg":"巴打 咁應該叫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教協1:30pm開記招 公佈反送中行動料回應罷課<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1201336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1201336</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\ncomment #255"},{"pid":"17f3fcecfad01783f0bdea72c70eea3c2c21d43e","tid":1393210,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0ab468e885c71c50bca2d12744ac9567bf99d44","tid":1393210,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05219218d7e0935080eeca82f8a81395a398ac5d","tid":1393210,"uid":66639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"蝴蝶效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />